headline: What DoorDash (DASH)'s Family Dollar Delivery Expansion Means For Shareholders
summary: DoorDash recently announced a partnership with Family Dollar, adding delivery from around 7,000 discount stores across the US to reach more value-conscious shoppers. headline: Palona AI Appoints Alison Templin as Vice President of Sales to Accelerate Enterprise Growth
summary: PALO ALTO, Calif., January 12, 2026--Palona AI, a leader in Real-World AI solutions for the restaurant industry, today announced the appointment of Alison Templin as Vice President of Sales. The hire strengthens Palona’s enterprise go-to-market leadership as the company scales its AI-powered platform across restaurant brands nationwide.
